{
  "id": "q7rNnpQc",
  "slug": "flower-pots",
  "title": "Flower Pots +",
  "description": "Giving Flower Pots the upgrade they deserve",
  "body": "![Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/043a8710d7ab36c4c87b9cb83cf43c9fe5e7a338.png)\n![Comparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fdfaa09891d5035651d5269842ddb71fd43a2597.gif)\n\n\n[![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/compact/available/curseforge_vector.svg)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/flower-pots)[![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/compact/available/modrinth_vector.svg)](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/flower-pots)[![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/c7fd18efdadd1c3f12ae56b49afd834640d2d797/assets/compact/social/discord-plural_vector.svg)](https://discord.gg/FgypubrVmn)\n\n***\n### **📋 About**\nFlower Pots + improves flower pots visually by **adding unique soil textures** depending on the plant and by **changing the texture of the flower pot block and item.**\n\n**The shading of all plants has been removed** so that they are as bright as their normal counterpart.\n\nAdditionally, **all flower pot models have been improved for better performance.**\n\nThe recent version of this pack is made for **Minecraft Version 1.20.x-1.21.x** and might not work with any other version.\n\n***\n\n### **✅ Recommendations**\nIf you want to have some very colourful and stylish flower pots, you should check out Colourful Pots:\n\n[![Colourful Pots](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/75by7BdO/4e9c5a162c82d959758f7b9dbe7a6ec5b0aefacc_96.webp)](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/colourful-pots)\n\nCheck out More Pots if you want to use Flower Pots + and Daggsy's packs:\n<br><br><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/more-pots\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f81e52e1b407d7fcd730c97dae50857ad1eaeb4c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\"></a>\n\nWant to check out more flower pot resource packs?\n\n[![Enhanced Flower Pots](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/jyZfZovk/edc9ff9871a9fee8ce3d6bd54af45d0bcd88dfc1_96.webp)](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/enhanced-flower-pots)\n\n***\n\n\n### **⚙️ Compatibility**\nFlower Pots + supports 80 different mods:\n\n<a title=\"Aether\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aether\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/867fcbfc1a39f450d19faf7e93247c4d553e1754_0.webp\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Alex's Caves\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alexs-caves\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/U6GY0xp0/4165eef78a7efa0f5acda964dd094c08ee0e5680.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Architect's Palette\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/architects-palette\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/332/416/64/64/637463465409763931_animated.gif\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Arts & Crafts\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/artsandcrafts\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/JI9mEkvq/ab8c87c86a7216bb8c064f1d9ebdbb00b56affc3.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Atmospheric\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/atmospheric\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/U9sJOFmJ/08e0ab9c03f182d557ee58216a3d2ae8304ff084_96.webp\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Autumnity\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/autumnity\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cRh6MJ6n/e52c9f8a03475093aed41835661de4e323fe1c42_96.webp\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Beautify\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/beautify-refabricated\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DhSSvaxs/c13d3f6a8ea281ecea904e10daa7d4de7147c22c.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"BetterDefaultBiomes\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-default-biomes\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/815/777/64/64/638192256011786159.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n<a title=\"Biome Makeover\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biome-makeover\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data